name: 01/01 Family House
description:
Meow Moon Village "Home that is aware of a cat needs"
A community developed for cats with various interests, the ideal home for cats with numerous hobbies. Our village is conveniently located in the city's center. Every home is custom constructed to fit each cat's preferences. Our project will contain only 50 cat houses. Cat Parks, Cat swimming pools, Cat spas, Cat restaurants, Cat fitness centers, Cat hair salons, and Cat training schools are all examples of places where cats can be found.
Don't lose out on the opportunity to join our village. We welcome you to a good society and will take good care of you.
